{"word":"H7618 - שְׁבוּ - shᵉbûw - sheb-oo' - Agate","slug":"H7618","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שְׁבוּ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shᵉbûw"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sheb-oo'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Agate"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05D5;&#x05BC; - sh<sup>e</sup>bu&#x0302;</b> - <i>sheb-oo'</i><p/>From an unused root (probably identical with that of <a href=\"#/H7617\">H7617</a> through the idea of <i>subdivision</i> into flashes or streamers (compare <a href=\"#/H7632\">H7632</a>)) meaning to <i>flame</i>; a <i>gem</i> (from its sparkle), probably the <i>agate: - </i>agate."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7617\">H7617</a>, <a href=\"#/H7619\">H7619</a>, <a href=\"#/H7622\">H7622</a>, <a href=\"#/H7628\">H7628</a>, <a href=\"#/H7629\">H7629</a>, <a href=\"#/H7630\">H7630</a>, <a href=\"#/H7633\">H7633</a>, <a href=\"#/H8453\">H8453</a>, <a href=\"#/H8664\">H8664</a>"}]}